 accepted
	

You should create a Desktop Entry first: Go in terminal and write:

sudo gedit /usr/share/applications/adt.desktop

and write inside of editor:

[Desktop Entry]
Name=ADT
Type=Application
Exec=/downloads/adt/eclipse/eclipse 
Terminal=false
Icon=/downloads/adt/eclipse/eclipse.xpm
Comment=Any comment
NoDisplay=false
Categories=Development;IDE
Name[en]=adt.desktop

save and exit
